name: Shaolin Wushu Club
description: Sima Azimi (23) from Afghanistan, trains a group of girls in the Shaolin Martial Arts to prepare for olympic competition but also to protect themselves on the streets of Kabul, where women are routinely harassed.  All the girls in the club are Hazara, a Persian-speaking, mainly Shiâ€™ite group who have faced a series of attacks claimed by ISIS militants over the past year.
